description: Flight delayed for more than 5 hours. causing missed connection. Long wait at the gate.
Luggage was lost during transfer and arrived 3 days late. Multiple complaints to customer service.
Security check caused delays. missed check-in time. The process was disorganized and frustrating.
Overcharged for seat selection on the flight. which was supposed to be free. No refund offered.
Flight was canceled last minute due to weather. No assistance or clear communication from the airline.
Bag arrived damaged and with broken items inside. Unable to claim compensation due to lack of documentation.
Airport security failed to handle the crowd. causing unnecessary stress and delays.
Rude behavior from flight attendants when I requested assistance. Felt ignored and disrespected.
Flight was overbooked and passengers were left stranded. No alternative arrangements made.
My suitcase was sent to the wrong destination and took 4 days to arrive.
X-ray scanner malfunctioned and delayed the process. Missed my connecting flight.
Charged extra for baggage despite being within the weight limit stated on the ticket.
Flight was delayed for more than 12 hours. and no compensation was offered.
Received my luggage. but it had been tampered with and items were missing.
Security line was disorganized. causing delays and missed flight.
Flight attendants were unhelpful when I asked for water during the flight.
Flight was rerouted due to a sudden technical issue. resulting in inconvenience.
Lost my luggage upon arrival. no information available about its location.
Security check was slow and inefficient. causing a delay in boarding.
Inadequate seating arrangement caused discomfort during the entire flight.
Missed my connecting flight due to delays on the initial leg of the trip.
Bag arrived with damaged straps. unable to claim any compensation from the airline.
X-ray machine malfunctioned. causing confusion and delays for all passengers.
In-flight entertainment system was broken for the entire flight.
The flight was delayed for more than 8 hours. and we were not informed of the status.
Bag arrived soaked due to mishandling. many of my personal items were damaged.
The security check process was inefficient and caused unnecessary delays.
Flight attendants were rude and uncooperative when I asked for assistance with my seat.
Flight was canceled without sufficient notice. causing significant inconvenience.
My luggage was sent to the wrong destination and delayed for over a week.
The security process took longer than expected. and I missed my connecting flight.
